    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is because you're using multiple hooks in a single component. That's an edge case that will be covered by https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/6660 and the `skipSuspense` option so that a second widget will be discoverable in the server.\n\nsolutions are thus:\n1. wait until the option is released\n2. patch InstantSearch yourself to include the code of #6660 \n3. use only one hook per component\n\nThe underlying reason for this happening is that we suspend at the first hook already, meaning the second widget in the same component won't be discovered.",
